title: Wallet 3

creator: ChainBow Co. Ltd.
descriptionHtml:
Wallet 3 is a digital wallet designed specifically for Ethereum users. It is both secure and user-friendly, allowing you to easily manage your Ethereum assets and view your balance, make transfers, and receive payments on the go. It also supports multiple cryptocurrencies, so you can manage all of your digital assets in one place. Whether you are an individual user or a business, Wallet 3 has you covered. Download Wallet 3 and enjoy a safe and convenient digital asset management experience.

1. Designed based on asset security.
2. All Layer2 and EVM-compatible chains are supported.
3. Built-in a powerful Web3 browser.
4. Fully open-source.
descriptionShort: A Secure Wallet for Web3 Era
